; Perfect forwarding predicate (ForwardsAllInputsAsIs): the identity arm
; a->b forwards all columns in order into b's UNION and can be substituted
; by its source; b's swap arm makes the union a real induction.

#message input(i32 A, i32 B).
#local a(i32 A, i32 B).
#local b(i32 A, i32 B).
#query out(free i32 A, free i32 B).

a(X, Y) : input(X, Y).
b(X, Y) : a(X, Y).
b(X, Y) : b(Y, X).
out(X, Y) : b(X, Y).
